{"tid":1604810,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[N區開花] 唔攻狗必救，係做唔到分散狗力效果，狗只會處理完必救先TG炸走你","createTime":"2019-09-30T05:36:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T07:12:15.000Z","uid":274475,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8b5b45397358df51b31a11098b77f2a66118ab48","tid":1604810,"uid":274475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:36:51.000Z","msg":"各位手足，做得N區開花，就係要令狗兵力不能集中，但大家一定要知道，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>如果響區內冇攻狗必救，狗係唔會理你住，只會集中搞掂其他區先再慢慢處理你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n如果大家記者728遮打遊行的話，應該會記得當日人龍分左兩邊，一邊行去中聯辦，一邊行去銅鑼灣。 當日狗係完全冇理銅鑼灣佔左成條路，銅鑼灣佔左半日狗影都唔見一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，啲狗集中清哂西環先慢慢搞銅鑼灣。<br />\n<br />\n攻狗之必救嘅方案未必個個一樣，可能係向政府地標大規模魔法，可能係大規模搞國旗國徽，<strong>可能係痛打未有增援嘅狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但大原則係如果你果區搞左一陣都冇狗到，即係對政權零威脅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，完全幫唔到其他區手足牽制警力，咁就要立即諗點升級先引到狗 </span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">十一國殤，賀佢老母</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d42040e602f4a9785c008920ee9a64437bc60fcd","tid":1604810,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T05:53:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ac8c265fbfdbe97e53c504be112b93111d54297","tid":1604810,"uid":260429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:58:28.000Z","msg":"true"},{"pid":"00a924f952f0d68d1a71557b5b6c8047724333e0","tid":1604810,"uid":36088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T06:59:39.000Z","msg":"agree"},{"pid":"41fafbb5900bf6d29192921f29c00b20dff8e57f","tid":1604810,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T07:05:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces